<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Altadore </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Given its close proximity to one of the best parks and the busiest outdoor shopping areas
                in Calgary, namely the River Park and Marda Loop respectively,</p>
            <p class="par-xl">the community in Altadore was named one of the cityâ€™s best neighborhoods in 2010. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Better known as the Marda Loop real estate district, Altadore homes for sale represent the
                hotbed of Calgary real estate. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The majority of the new Calgary in-fills being constructed are the subdivision of
                Altadore. The SW Calgary subdivision of Altadore is ideally situated for the city core worker who likes
                to be close to the action, but not right in the heart of it.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located on a plateau above the Elbow River (Sandy Beach) and bordering South Calgary, New
                Altadore homeowners will love trendy shops, amazing restaurants and coffee shops and the dog walks in
                the park. </p>


